  "prompt": "Is the driver job in Uber considered as work experience when applying for higher studies abroad?",
  "response": "Yes, being a driver for Uber can be considered work experience when applying for higher studies abroad. When describing this experience in your application, it\u2019s important to highlight the skills and attributes you\u2019ve developed through the role, such as customer service, time management, problem-solving, and communication skills. While it may not be directly related to your field of study, it demonstrates your ability to hold a job, manage responsibilities, and interact with a diverse range of people. Make sure to provide context and emphasize any transferable skills that are relevant to the academic program you\u2019re applying to.",
